rows.label: tlk43700149_04_msg0001
rows.name:
No time to be worrying about
Invidia or Superbia or what
your pals think of you now...

rows.label: tlk43700149_04_msg0002
rows.name:
At this rate, we'll all be
going down together...

rows.label: tlk43700149_04_msg0003
rows.name:
And at this late stage, I
finally realized something.

rows.label: tlk43700149_04_msg0004
rows.name:
That all this would never have
happened if we'd just worked
together from the start.

rows.label: tlk43700149_04_msg0005
rows.name:
But that's always the case in
hindsight, isn't it? This is a lesson
we'd never have learned otherwise.
